channel.title: Malaysian jetliner shot down by surface-to-air missile over Ukraine
channel.description: Malaysian Airlines passenger plane en route from Amsterdam to Kuala Lumpur with 295 aboard, is shot down by a surface-to-air missile in Ukraine near the Russian border, Fox News confirms.
